enum MCTM_COMUS_Enum

Enumeration of MCTM COMUS.

Enumerator:
MCTM_COMUS_STIOFF 

MCTM capture/compare control bits are updated by setting the UEV2G bit only

MCTM_COMUS_STION 

MCTM capture/compare control bits are updated by both setting the UEV2G bit or when a rising edge occurs on STI

enum TM_SMSEL_Enum

Enumeration of TM slave mode selection.

Enumerator:
TM_SMSEL_DISABLE 

The prescaler is clocked directly by the internal clock

TM_SMSEL_DECODER1 

Counter counts up/down on CH0 edge depending on CH1 level

TM_SMSEL_DECODER2 

Counter counts up/down on CH1 edge depending on CH0 level

TM_SMSEL_DECODER3 

Counter counts up/down on both CH0 & CH1 edges depending on the level of the other input

TM_SMSEL_PAUSE 

Slave pause mode

TM_SMSEL_TRIGGER

TM_SMSEL_STIED
